data.description: Welcome to a fantastic 4-bed, 2.5-bath two-story home designed for comfort and enjoyment. The living room boasts high ceilings and a charming brick fireplace, creating a warm atmosphere for gatherings. The updated kitchen features granite countertops, with a dining room and a cozy breakfast area, offering both formal and casual dining options. The upstairs connects seamlessly to the living room below, welcoming natural light throughout the home.    Outside, discover a backyard oasis with a large pool for refreshing dips, a covered patio for outdoor relaxation, and a fire pit for cozy evenings. Enjoy the spacious yard with beautiful views of the adjacent golf course. This home is a perfect blend of comfort, style, and outdoor appeal—an ideal setting for your family. Explore the ease and joy of living in this well-designed space. Welcome home!
